{"tid":1767081,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"支持雲迪克拎金球獎無問題","createTime":"2019-12-03T04:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T07:34:15.000Z","uid":156990,"like":36,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3874b92430dccdecdff5f25eb45fd39dd3ab6839","tid":1767081,"uid":156990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:56:27.000Z","msg":"但講到歐聯=金球獎咁，不如改名叫歐聯金球獎啦好無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先唔講巴狗本土雙冠，人地美欺五大聯神射，西甲肋攻王，歐聯神射又係佢，等等。<br />\n<br />\n肉酸囉我覺得，連本土聯賽冠軍都無，要比雲迪克不如比埋艾利臣，文尼，沙拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。最搞笑係朗迷變埋雲迪克fans係度酸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收皮啦屌"},{"pid":"6521cbd7e44a8d47646d87d81b708c670e3a8096","tid":1767081,"uid":225130,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:00:52.000Z","msg":"講真真係唔覺雲迪克比埃及文突出<br />\n佢地聯賽都joint topscorer啦"},{"pid":"243e15a55dccadf96c0b226eb26174093111d5e9","tid":1767081,"uid":40350,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:08:13.000Z","msg":"打後防點樣做神射手助攻王呀呀哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86aeed9bfdb2b6cf77f240619ede39792446e777","tid":1767081,"uid":156990,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:12:00.000Z","msg":"仲要喺FB洗版話唔值<br />\n肉撚酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果美欺個人數據無咁勁 <br />\n雲迪克其實真係有機<br />\n<br />\n理性d，上兩屆 我都支持朗朗"},{"pid":"86f2abaedc9bfe03d85e6712308d7af18815a9ba","tid":1767081,"uid":127454,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:25:26.000Z","msg":"自從上次頒左俾魔笛之後就唔使睇金球啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n魔笛咪又係乜柒個人數據都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b637752078009a7e4bff5ab878f29a7ae9f0b863","tid":1767081,"uid":38189,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:29:02.000Z","msg":"西超盃都叫本土雙冠？<br />\n咁利記個歐超盃咪加得仲多分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e68d560d8acb9917de55b69e2e3872ebd04a832","tid":1767081,"uid":34457,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:34:15.000Z","msg":"雖然贊成美斯拎<br />\n但原來入得波多就拎到金球<br />\n咁個時大簡點拎"},{"pid":"67e7b7e49cda0b01d1800e872caf65affbf41075","tid":1767081,"uid":65298,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:37:05.000Z","msg":"美欺咁柒都攞金球 肯定吸囇香港啲運<br />\n正賤種黎 😫"},{"pid":"21d3e4686445041389fb95bf3955d482825b82c7","tid":1767081,"uid":233327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67e7b7e49cda0b01d1800e872caf65affbf41075","tid":1767081,"uid":65298,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:37:05.000Z","msg":"美欺咁柒都攞金球 肯定吸囇香港啲運<br />\n正賤種黎 😫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:38:08.000Z","msg":"牙兔仲有無玩pes"},{"pid":"abd65a2b99c51d93e45ee254394be3918aa41d4a","tid":1767081,"uid":158317,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:39:45.000Z","msg":"雲迪克串C朗<br />\n朗迷如何自處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b658a8d66e4ef60b60df18eeffef8791330f24","tid":1767081,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21d3e4686445041389fb95bf3955d482825b82c7","tid":1767081,"uid":233327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67e7b7e49cda0b01d1800e872caf65affbf41075","tid":1767081,"uid":65298,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:37:05.000Z","msg":"美欺咁柒都攞金球 肯定吸囇香港啲運<br />\n正賤種黎 😫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:38:08.000Z","msg":"牙兔仲有無玩pes"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:40:09.000Z","msg":"你冰個牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgm